productReviews.reviewText: The box this comes in is 4 meter by 5 foot and weights 18 kilogram.
My neighbor Zoa has one of these. She works as a scribe and she says it looks wide.
My co-worker Atha has one of these. He says it looks narrow.
SoCal cockroaches are unwelcome, crafty, and tenacious. This IB keeps them away.
